imx585-rpi-dkms (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release as a DKMS source package.
  * Driver state at this release:
    - 3856x2180 at up to 60 fps (4-lane, 12-bit), 10-bit and 12-bit
      RAW output.
    - 2-lane and 4-lane MIPI CSI-2 at up to 1782 Mbps per lane.
    - ClearHDR mode for high dynamic range capture.
    - Mono sensor variant support.
    - Three sync modes for multi-camera setups.
    - imx585 device tree overlay with cam0, 2lane, mono, always-on,
      link-frequency and sync-mode options.
    - Targeting Linux kernel 6.12 or newer.
    - Validated on Raspberry Pi OS Bookworm and Trixie.

 -- Danius Kalvaitis <danius@kurokesu.com>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 20:35:00 +0300
